text: Subin Limbu () (born 1 March 1991) in Dharan, Nepal is a Nepali Model and the title winner of the beauty pageant Miss Nepal 2014. She also represented Nepal in Miss World 2014. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Nepalese beauty pageant winners Category:Nepalese models Category:Miss Nepal winners
